>4,4′-Diaminodifenylmetan (4,4′-Metylendianilin)</td><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">101-77-9</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">10</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">3,3′-Diklorbensidin</td><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">91-94-1</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">11</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">3,3′-Dimetoksybensidin, (o-dianisidin)</td><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">119-90-4</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">12</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">3,3 Dimetylbensidin, (4,4′-Bi-o-toluidin)</td><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">119-93-7</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">13</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">4,4′-Metylendi-o-toluidin, (4,4′-Metylenbis, 2-metylanilin)</td><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">838-88-0</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">14</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">p-Cresidin (6-metoksimetylanilin)</td><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">120-71-8</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">15</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">2,2-Diklor-4,4′-metylendianilin (4,4′-Metylenbis, 2-kloranilin)</td><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">101-14-4</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">16</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">4,4′-Oksidianilin (4,4′Diaminodifenyleter)</td><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">101-80-4</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">17</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">4,4′-Tiodianilin</td><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">139-65